MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2018-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 23rd August, 2018
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 23rd August, 2018:
i)
Shri Piyush Goyal relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the
charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs held by him. Shri Piyush Goyal
will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Railways and the charge of
the office of the Minister of Coal;
ii)
Shri Arun Jaitley relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister without Portfolio
and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the charge of the
office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs.
र३.१.1
(Manoj Kumar Bansal)
